y paid under the wrong head. Despite a slight delay in his refund application, the court ruled that the inadvertent error and unused stamps meant the government couldn't unjustly enrich itself.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/regulatory/bombay-hc-orders-3-lakh-refund-for-homebuyer-due-to-stamp-duty-error/130814968?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-31462/130814968.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "regulatory"}]}